These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, fanta, soy-milk, iced-tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the car and the person driving the motorbike##2
6. the person drinking iced-tea is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | tea     | soy-milk | fanta |
| Transport     | bike     | motorbike | roller  | car      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, reading, video-games, skydiving
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, snowmobile, trike
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Hobby   | puzzles | reading    | skydiving     | video-games  |
| Transport     | bus    | snowmobile | helicopter | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, jazz, pop, rock
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, scientific, western, superhero
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
2. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | pop   | house  | rock |
| Movie-Genre           | scientific | superhero | western | romance  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, begonia, bellflower, daisy
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, egyptian, indian
1. the indian is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is between the person who growsorchid and the egyptian##2
3. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
4. the egyptian is on the left or right of the indian##3
5. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the argentine is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Flower         | begonia | orchid | daisy | bellflower  |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | argentine   | indian  | egyptian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, r&b, disco, soul
1. the fan of r&b is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the fan of soul is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | 7up    | fanta   | hot-chocolate | soy-milk    |
| Music-Genre      | r&b | folk | disco       | soul |

