.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, may, february, april
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, roller, train, tram
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person driving the train is between the person driving the tram and the person who's birthday is in february##2
3. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the train and the person who's birthday is in october##2
4. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Birthday    | october | february | april | may |
| Transport   | roller | boat  | train    | tram  |

