.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, november, march, february
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, ship, snowmobile, van
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in february##2
5. the person driving the ship is the person driving the ship##1
6. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person who's birthday is in february##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | september | february | march | november     |
| Transport     | airplane | van  | ship   | snowmobile |

