.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, tea, mirinda, water
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, skiing, tennis, volleyball
1. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking tea is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is basketball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage     | cola | tea   | mirinda      | water      |
| Sport   | skiing     | tennis | basketball | volleyball |

