.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
City: edinburgh, prague, marseilles, colone
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, nigerian, russian
1. the argentine is on the right of the chinese##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is between the russian and the chinese##2
3. the person traveling to prague is the chinese##1
4. the nigerian is on the left of the chinese##1
5. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the argentine##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| City   | edinburgh | prague | marseilles      | colone   |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | chinese    | argentine | russian |

