2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the tram is the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
5. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
6. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage       | 7up | mirinda | almond-milk    | hot-chocolate      |
| Transport   | taxi       | tram       | snowmobile | skateboard |

