.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, reggae, jazz, d&b
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, frog, hamster
1. the fan of reggae is on the far right##1
2. the fan of salsa is the fan of salsa##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
5. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
6. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
7. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | jazz  | d&b | reggae |
| Pet           | frog     | hamster | bird    | fish     |

