.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, horror, satire, zombie
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, librarian, manager, musician
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the librarian##3
2. the librarian is on the right of the manager##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the bartender##1
4. the librarian is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person watching satire movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror  | fantasy | zombie  | satire      |
| Job    | musician | bartender | manager | librarian |

