.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, collecting, dancing, rock-climbing
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, frog, horse
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is the owner of the horse##1
4. the owner of the ferret is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
6. the owner of the frog is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting | rock-climbing | dancing | card-games |
| Pet   | horse     | chinchilla       | ferret   | frog      |

