House: palace, farmhouse, modern, gothic-revival
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
4. the farmhouse house is on the right of the palace house##1
5. the modern house is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | cola    | milk  | fanta |
| House   | palace       | farmhouse | modern | gothic-revival  |

