4 different games are played: bridge, chess, billiard, poker
1. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
2. the person watching horror movies is the person playing poker##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
4. the person watching spy movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person playing billiard is between the person watching spy movies and the person playing poker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | horror  | animation  | spy |
| Game           | bridge    | poker | billiard | chess |

