.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-19::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, papaya, plum, pumpkin
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, sailing, tennis, climbing
1. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person eating plum##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Food   | pumpkin        | orange       | plum   | papaya |
