.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, milk, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, soul, pop, jazz
1. the fan of pop is on the far right##1
2. the fan of jazz is the fan of jazz##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
4. the fan of metal is on the far left or far right##3
5. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
6. the fan of metal is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta     | cola     | milk          | soy-milk |
| Music-Genre      | metal | soul | jazz | pop  |

 